---
title: Middle Eastern-Spiced Chicken Mezze with Honey-Glazed Haloumi, Flatbreads & Dips
description: Turn a weeknight meal into a fun feast with this mixed platter of Middle Eastern chicken, honey-glazed haloumi, hummus and a colourful and refreshing salsa. Toasted flatbreads add the perfect finishing touch for a feast of tasty treats where every bite is different.

*We’ve replaced the hummus in this recipe with tahini due to local
ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
